originalText.text: I had my daughters birthday here. She wanted a glow in the dark disco party. I have say from beginning to end everyone I dealt with at The East wing was fabulous. I HIGHLY recommend renting this room for a private event! We will definitely use them next time we need a private space again!

originalText.text:
I cannot say any more fantastic things about the East doing and Josh the owner. It was a fantastic place to hold my wedding reception! Everybody has such a fantastic time, the food was fantastic, the staff were great, and the bartenders and drinks where the best!
Eat drink and be merry event planners that do the planning for the Stumble Inn/ the East wing make sure that my husband and I were 100% comfortable and how much money we spent, the allowed us to pick and choose however we wanted to split our Monies for food and drink, and also make sure that if we wanted bigger tables or smaller tables anything at all we were happy and taken care of.
I now know a wonderful place not too far from my job to bring staff for lunch dinner parties or just for a few drinks. Whatever it is or whatever events I have planned for my future I will be thinking and making sure that I make the East wing my first choice in venues.
I have already been talkin this place up to anyone who has something that they want to celebrate. I will be coming back!
Josh thank you again for meeting with us that day when we went to talk about tables and how to arrange them in the room and for the wonderful little wedding gift that you provided to our reception. We were all having a ball using it!
